+ ./convert -h
convert - Sample application using default arguments and flags

Usage:
  convert [SOURCE] [options]
  convert --help | -h
  convert --version | -v

Options:
  --help, -h
    Show this help

  --version, -v
    Show version number

  --format, -f FORMAT
    Format to convert to
    Default: png

Arguments:
  SOURCE
    Files to convert
    Default: *.jpg

Examples:
  convert *.bmp
  convert --format jpg
  convert *.bmp --format jpg

